ic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209680/extras/c856deba551fcf03ebe824a32b65a501.poster.avif?t=1760716065\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209680/extras/c856deba551fcf03ebe824a32b65a501.webm?t=1760716065\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209680/extras/c856deba551fcf03ebe824a32b65a501.mp4?t=1760716065\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Ability to call artillery strikes and rain destruction on your enemies.<br>Getting temporary upgrades on your weapons which include Poison Gas, Armor Piercing, Explosive and Incendiary ammunition.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209680/extras/a2c5e256c14c09b19b4cf806ae6d8dee.poster.avif?t=1760716065\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209680/extras/a2c5e256c14c09b19b4cf806ae6d8dee.webm?t=1760716065\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209680/extras/a2c5e256c14c09b19b4cf806ae6d8dee.mp4?t=1760716065\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Strengthening your defenses with anti-personnel and anti-tank mines, explosive barrels, tank barriers and barbed wire.<br>Earn medals for achieving diffferent actions as you progress.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209680/extras/e66f2065a5f77b04b8b0881d9504bee4.poster.avif?t=1760716065\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209680/extras/e66f2065a5f77b04b8b0881d9504bee4.webm?t=1760716065\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/s